re's a change in the epithelial cells.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036831,0.067267,0.084127,0.095954,0.10234,0.10344,0.10476,0.10047,0.092891,0.084406,0.070212,0.057298],"unified_progress":[0.0381,0.070939,0.089318,0.10201,0.10573,0.11156,0.10354,0.096116,0.090736,0.080649,0.063043,0.048261]},{"section":9,"text":"But wait, Barrett's usually involves intestinal metaplasia, which isn't mentioned here.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029042,0.057022,0.075285,0.088136,0.09869,0.10309,0.10869,0.10761,0.10195,0.092592,0.077497,0.060394],"unified_progress":[0.033274,0.065109,0.085754,0.098299,0.10399,0.11097,0.10536,0.10025,0.094811,0.086388,0.067361,0.048433]},{"section":10,"text":"Instead, the biopsy shows upward extension of the papillae of the lamina propria.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029194,0.065856,0.085854,0.1011,0.107,0.10716,0.10937,0.0995,0.091371,0.077109,0.067826,0.05866],"unified_progress":[0.032005,0.072043,0.094284,0.10883,0.11407,0.10796,0.10322,0.094635,0.096322,0.072479,0.05787,0.046281]},{"section":11,"text":"That sounds like something is going on with the connective tissue beneath the epithelium.","dimension":17,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036573,0.079636,0.097128,0.10854,0.10543,0.10178,0.099482,0.092603,0.08449,0.074643,0.064378,0.055325],"unified_progress":[0.03248,0.069441,0.090417,0.10416,0.10833,0.10655,0.10637,0.097826,0.09323,0.080538,0.063256,0.047405]},{"section":12,"text":"Also, there's an increased number of neutrophils and lymphocytes, which suggests some kind of inflammation.","dimension":1,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03649,0.070639,0.089782,0.10159,0.10502,0.10396,0.10184,0.095558,0.089093,0.079654,0.069251,0.057123],"unified_progress":[0.038462,0.073149,0.091758,0.10136,0.10685,0.10492,0.10238,0.09616,0.090695,0.080117,0.065519,0.048627]},{"section":13,"text":"Putting this tog